{"tid":1661674,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"28年前炒的士牌柒左，果年就應該移民啦閪婆","createTime":"2019-10-18T08:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T03:17:56.000Z","uid":89349,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"55c7581c45976c7d2c3d20ea826b685645ae3a0a","tid":1661674,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T08:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Gbay3Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Gbay3Z.jpg&h=81fa7f8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>譚惠珠於<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">早年</span>任議員時，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">立場為傾向英國政府</span>的一方，在香港逐漸臨近主權移交的期間卻成為支持中國政府的一員。</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"></span><br />\n<strong>1990年7月，《壹週刊》揭發譚惠珠身為交通諮詢委員會主席，竟然擁有從事的士牌炒賣活動的「先達的士公司」股份，而且未有申報該利益。由於事件涉及利益衝突[10][11]，更因事件被無綫新聞跟進，而向無綫主席邵逸夫申訴，掀起一場干預新聞自由風波[12]<br />\n<br />\n令<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">當時港英政府逐漸與她疏遠</span></strong>，事件成了她政治生涯轉捩點。1991年，譚惠珠不再獲委任為行政局議員、立法局議員及交通諮詢委員會主席，<span style=\"color: red;\">最後因誠信破產而一度被迫淡出政壇</span>。</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n遲頭草，垃撚圾</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%AD%9A%E6%83%A0%E7%8F%A0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%25AD%259A%25E6%2583%25A0%25E7%258F%25A0&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz6VNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=052eafd2\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%AD%9A%E6%83%A0%E7%8F%A0</a>"},{"pid":"87a9e83e65f01eb6dc889ea93cd6f2f1cc60f953","tid":1661674,"uid":301523,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T08:54:29.000Z","msg":"英國佬唔會要D做完污糟野有醜聞既人<br />\n<br />\n但係共產黨偏偏好鐘意用 因為佢地有痛腳係手一定會聽聽話話<br />\n<br />\n仲有一個例子就係689"},{"pid":"b9bfdda2890f61d96ac0009babe5de91f46b929e","tid":1661674,"uid":29080,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"87a9e83e65f01eb6dc889ea93cd6f2f1cc60f953","tid":1661674,"uid":301523,"